-- Madrid May Boost Transport Ticket to Cut Deficit, Expansion Says
-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 2012-03-21T07:22:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-21/madrid-may-boost-transport-ticket-to-cut-deficit-expansion-says.html
Madrid ’s  regional government  may
increase the cost of transport tickets as part of measures to
reduce its deficit, Expansion reported.  Tax revenue last year declined by about 1 billion euros
($1.33 billion) below the administration’s estimates, Expansion
said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
